==Russian==

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''[[что]]-[[либо]]''' (štó-libo)
:'''N.B.''' &mdash; the particle -[[либо]] imparts a stronger sense of indefiniteness than [[-то]] or [[-нибудь]].

# [[anything]], [[something]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[знать|Зна́ете]] [[ли#Russian|ли]] [[вы]] что́-либо [[об]] [[этот|э́том]]?}} — ''Do you know anything about this?''

